        image: image_path("modules/site/codespaces/katie.jpg"),
        title: "Staff Developer, TELUS",
      }, {
        quote: "Before Codespaces, the onboarding process was tedious. Instead of taking two days, now it only takes a minute for a developer to access a pristine, steady-state environment, thanks to prebuilds.",
